data.description:
St. Cloud, FL 

Furnishing Gone
Immaculate Condition 
“Move in Ready”

Price: $524,900

5 Bedrooms
3.5 Bathrooms
2,790sf

Located at the new Osprey Cove community, Harmony West, this better than new this 5 bedroom, 3.5 bathroom home with a two-car garage is move in ready. 

This "Lucerne" model includes luxury features throughout and has a little of everything from ceramic plank tile flooring to open kitchen design stainless whirlpool appliances, 42-inch cabinets, quartz countertops in both kitchen and bathrooms, as well as a separate laundry room. 

The exterior features brick pavers, covered and screened outdoor living that leads to the perfect sized backyard. Plenty of double pane insulated screened windows to let the Florida sunshine in! 

Situated across from the playground and dog park, you'll find yourself comfortably settling into this new home and community. Ideally located far enough to get away but close enough to enjoy dining, entertainment and shopping. Only minutes to Florida Turnpike, Melbourne beach and Kissimmee. 

Harmony West:
Theres no other community quite like Harmony West-where life comes into balance. 

This community celebrates the best of small-town peaceful living, in a convenient location where youll take advantage of all Central Florida has to offer. 

This is a community where neighbors know each other and kids aren't the only ones who get to play. 

Features of this community include top rated K-12 schools, sparkling natural pond and nearby lakes, local Johnny Miller Signature golf course and lifestyle activities the whole family will enjoy. When you're surrounded by nature, you want nothing more than to get outside. 

Community amenities include a resort style clubhouse and pool with lounge seating, playground, amphitheater, and park space. Residents are drawn to this incredible community for its serene outdoor surroundings including walking, biking, and local equestrian trail recreation offered. Nearby Town Square offers activities, eateries, shops and a weekly farmers market. 

This community lies just 20 minutes to Lake Nona Medical City, 25 minutes to the Orlando International Airport, 30 minutes to Disney World and 40 minutes to the Atlantic beaches.
